wikipedia_page.main: Zachariah John Chappell (born 21 August 1996) is an English cricketer who plays for Nottinghamshire County Cricket Club. He is a right-arm fast-medium bowler who also bats right-handed. He made his Twenty20 debut for Leicestershire County Cricket Club against Northamptonshire in July 2015.
